column4: PRESS DIGEST- Wall Street Journal - May 1
column5: May 1 The following are the top stories in the Wall Street Journal. Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy.

column4: UPDATE 1-U.S. SEC commissioner decries agency's deal with Tesla's Musk
column5: April 30 A U.S. Securities and Exchange commissioner on Tuesday criticized a settlement between the regulator and Tesla Inc  CEO Elon Musk over his use of Twitter.

column4: Judge approves Musk  SEC agreement over Twitter use by CEO
column5: NEW YORK  April 30 A federal judge on Tuesday approved a deal struck between Tesla Inc Chief Executive Elon Musk and the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission over Musk's use of Twitter  a court filing showed.

column4: Qualcomm hangs on to most Apple gains after earnings report
column5: Qualcomm Inc shares fell about 3% on Wednesday as investors got their first look at the bottom line impact of a patent fight settlement with Apple Inc.
